## Price Comparison: Cushion vs Radiant (1ct, Blue Nile {{year}})

At equivalent quality grades, cushion modified brilliants are typically 15–30% less expensive than radiant cuts. This gap is most pronounced at the G-F colour tier. At the D colour tier at 1ct, cushion and radiant are surprisingly close in price.

